## BallerApp

- **App**: court discovery, ranked games, tournaments
- **Flutter**: `baller_app/pubspec.yaml` (SDK `^3.9.0`) · Maps · geolocator
- **Backend**: `backend/app/main.py` FastAPI + PostGIS (`docker-compose.dev.yml`)
- **Entry**: `baller_app/lib/main.dart` → `BadwordFilter` → `AuthGate()`
- **Data layer**: `baller_app/lib/repositories/` · `baller_app/lib/core/api/` (API mode) · legacy `lib/supabase/court_services.dart`

